summary: Makes you jump 2, 5, 10, 20, 50 or 100 times higher, depending on your choice.
descriptionHtml:
[size=20]Superjump[/size]
Makes you jump 2, 5, 10, 20, 50 or 100 times higher, depending on your choice.

[b]Installation:[/b]
Extract only [b]one[/b] .esp file into your Skyrim\'s data folder. Enable it from launcher.

[b]Known bugs:[/b]
You can \"escape\" from cities into surrounding enviroments, which may cause all sorts of crazy bugs.

Extremely experimental, may destroy your save, computer or the whole space-time continuum.
author: simssi
